==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unkiss
<hw>Un*kiss"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>king</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cancel or annul what
was done or sealed by a kiss; to cancel by a kiss.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let me <qex>unkiss</qex> the oath 'twixt thee and me.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unkle</ent>⟦br⟧
